OL,3,CMan fined after stealing luggage from
OL,4,Cbreastfeeding mother at airport
OL,6,FA 52-year-old man has been fined after
OL,7,Fadmitting stealing luggage from a
OL,8,Fmother while she breastfed her
OL,9,Fdaughter at an airport.
OL,11,FJohn Brooks, 52, of Brighton Road,
OL,12,FCrawley, has pleaded guilty to
OL,13,Fstealing a suitcase and a child's
OL,14,Fbackpack from Gatwick Airport on
OL,15,FOctober 30 2025.
OL,17,FHe also admitted causing criminal
OL,18,Fdamage worth #88.30 for breaking a
OL,19,Fsecurity barrier with his head as he
OL,20,Fescaped with the luggage.
