OL,6,FOn Tuesday, Brooks appeared at Crawley
OL,7,FMagistrates Court wearing an orange
OL,8,Fcoat under a black gilet and spoke to
OL,9,Fconfirm his name, date of birth and
OL,10,Faddress.
OL,12,FAfter entering his pleas he heard
OL,13,Fabout the impact on his victim, before
OL,14,Fbeing fined #388.30 by the magistrates
OL,15,Fbench.
OL,17,FThe mother-of-two went to the baby
OL,18,Fcare room in the South Terminal of
OL,19,FGatwick Airport to breastfeed her
OL,20,Fyounger daughter.
