OL,6,F"Due to the way the room is laid out
OL,7,Fshe wasn't able to bring her pram and
OL,8,Fluggage outside the room so left it
OL,9,Fjust outside the door," said Amy
OL,10,FFraser, prosecuting.
OL,12,FBrooks, who appeared drunk, then
OL,13,Farrived and stood by her luggage
OL,14,Ftrolley for a "short time" outside the
OL,15,Ftoilets before taking it and moving
OL,16,Foff, the court heard.
