OL,6,FMs Fraser said: "He goes through the
OL,7,Ftaxi area and then down to where the
OL,8,Fexit of the car park is... he ducks
OL,9,Fdown to go under the barrier but it
OL,10,Fwon't move so he uses his head to move
OL,11,Fthe barrier which then bends and
OL,12,Fbreaks."
OL,14,FThe prosecution called it an
OL,15,F"opportunistic crime" and said the
OL,16,Fluggage was later recovered and
OL,17,Freturned.
