OL,6,FIn a victim impact statement, the
OL,7,Fmother said she now feels "insecure"
OL,8,Fin public, and that her older
OL,9,Fdaughter, eight, has become fearful.
OL,11,F"What happened has changed the way we
OL,12,Ffeel in public spaces, the way we
OL,13,Ftravel and the way my daughter sees
OL,14,Fthe world around her," she said.
OL,16,FBrooks has 37 previous convictions for
OL,17,F72 offences, 42 of which relate to
OL,18,Ftheft.
